    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei aeterni. <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/79"
                            >Hugo</persName> et <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/72"
                            >Lotharius</persName> divina providente clementia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">reges</rs>. Si praedia ecclesiarum Dei largis
                        augmentamus muneribus, largiora aeternae vitae praemia consequi minime
                        dubitamus. Quocirca omnium fidelium sanctae Dei Ecclesiae nostrorumque
                        praesentium ac futurorum devotio noverit, qualiter pro Dei amore animarumque
                        nostrarum et <persName key="#parentOf" ref="#people/1526"
                            >Tetbaldi</persName> avi seu genitoris nostri nec non <persName><name
                                ref="Berilio">Berilionis</name></persName> patris <persName><name
                                ref="Ingelbertus">Ingelberti</name></persName> remedio offerimus Deo
                        et <rs
                            key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesiae</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1439" key="#Curtes #Houses #Natural_landscape #Rivers #Mountains #Curtes #Mansi #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius">Beati Mauricii martyris
                            Christi</orgName> fundatae <placeName ref="#places/1893"
                            >Viennae</placeName>, ubi <persName key="#Archbishops"><name ref="Sobo"
                                >Sobo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Archbishops">archiepiscopus</rs> praeesse videtur, ac per hoc
                        nostrum praeceptum, prout iuste et legaliter possumus, donamus atque
                        largimur <rs key="#Curtes">cortem</rs> unam <rs key="#Fiscal_property">iuris
                            nostri</rs> quae <geogName
                            key="#Houses #Natural_landscape #Rivers #Mountains #Curtes #Mansi #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius"
                            >Casteneto</geogName> inferiore nuncupatur superiore positam in <rs
                            key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/2307">Viennensi</geogName>, una cum
                            <rs key="#Mansi">mansis</rs>, <rs key="#Houses">casis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Cereals">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">pascuis</rs>, <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Fisheries">piscariis</rs>, <rs key="#Mills">molendinis</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Natural_landscape">diversisque territoriis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Mountains">montibus</rs>, <rs key="#Natural_landscape"
                            >vallibus</rs>, <rs key="#Mountains">alpibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Natural_landscape">planitiebus</rs>, <rs key="#Rivers">aquis
                            aquarumve decursibus</rs> universisque appenditiis, <rs
                            key="#Royal_slave">servis quoque et ancillis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Royal_aldius">aldionibus et aldiabus</rs> ad ipsam cortem et res
                        aspicientibus in integrum, ac <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >de nostro iure et dominio in prefatae ecclesiae ius et dominium omnino
                            transfundimus ac delegamus</rs>, ut in perpetuum habeat, possideat et
                        fruatur iure quieto, omnium hominum controversia remota. Si quis igitur hanc
                        nostri praecepti oblationem invadere aut infringere tentaverit, noverit se
                        compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">auri optimi libras ducentas</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Camera_regis">medietatem camerae regiae</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem prefatae ecclesiae
                            et episcopo qui inibi pro tempore fuerit</rs>; insuper cum Iuda
                        traditore aeterna damnatione mulctetur, et in praesens anathematis iaculo
                        feriatur. Quod ut verius credatur diligentiusque ab omnibus observetur,
                        manibus propriis roborantes anulo nostro insigniri iussimus. Signa
                        serenissorum (M) (M) Hugonis et Lotharii regum. <persName
                            key="#Chancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/1535">Giseprandus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> et <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs>
                        ad vicem <persName key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/1531"
                            >Bosonis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovi et subscripsi. Data octavo kalendas
                        februarii, anno dominicae incarnationis DCCCCXLV, regni vero domni Hugonis
                        XVIII, Lotharii XIIII, indictione tertia. Actum <placeName ref="#places/65"
                            >Papiae</placeName>. Feliciter, amen.</ab>
